&lt;p>&lt;strong>Part 3 of the &lt;em>Human Skills, AI-Expanded&lt;/em> series&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>HR and people leaders carry work that is both &lt;strong>data-heavy&lt;/strong> and &lt;strong>deeply human&lt;/strong>. Workforce plans, hiring pipelines, performance cycles, and reorganizations generate long documents and strong emotions. AI can speed up reading, structuring, and drafting—but it cannot own &lt;strong>fairness, trust, or final people decisions&lt;/strong>.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>